---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us | Ocala Golf Cart Rentals">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-600 to-emerald-800 text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
        About Ocala Golf Cart Rentals
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-emerald-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Your trusted local partner for premium golf cart rentals in the Horse Capital of the World.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Story</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Born and raised in Ocala, we understand the unique charm and beauty of our city. After years of watching visitors struggle to explore all that Ocala has to offer, we decided to create a better way to experience our hometown.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Ocala Golf Cart Rentals was founded with a simple mission: to provide comfortable, reliable, and fun transportation that allows both visitors and locals to discover Ocala's hidden gems, historic downtown, beautiful parks, and world-renowned horse country.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
            Today, we're proud to be Ocala's premier golf cart rental service, offering top-quality vehicles and exceptional customer service that reflects the warm hospitality our city is known for.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-400 to-emerald-600 rounded-lg h-96 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-white text-xl font-semibold">Ocala's Premier Golf Cart Rental Service</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Our Values
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          What drives us to provide exceptional service every day
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-emerald-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Community First</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We're not just a business - we're part of the Ocala community. We support local events, charities, and work to make our city even better.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-emerald-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Quality & Safety</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Every golf cart in our fleet is meticulously maintained and regularly inspected to ensure your safety and comfort during your rental.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-emerald-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Exceptional Service</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">From the moment you book until you return your cart, we're here to ensure your experience is smooth, enjoyable, and memorable.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team Section -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Meet Our Team
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          Local experts who know Ocala inside and out
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-400 to-emerald-600 rounded-full w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-white text-2xl font-bold">JD</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">John Davis</h3>
          <p class="text-emerald-600 font-medium mb-2">Founder & Owner</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Born and raised in Ocala, John started this business to share his love for the city with visitors and locals alike.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-400 to-emerald-600 rounded-full w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-white text-2xl font-bold">SM</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Sarah Martinez</h3>
          <p class="text-emerald-600 font-medium mb-2">Operations Manager</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Sarah ensures every golf cart is in perfect condition and every customer has an exceptional experience.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-400 to-emerald-500 rounded-full w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-white text-2xl font-bold">MR</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Mike Rodriguez</h3>
          <p class="text-emerald-600 font-medium mb-2">Customer Service Lead</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Mike is your go-to person for recommendations on where to visit and how to make the most of your time in Ocala.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-emerald-600 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">
        Ready to Experience Ocala?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 text-emerald-100">
        Join thousands of satisfied customers who have explored Ocala with us.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg transition-colors inline-block">
        Book Your Rental Today
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
